    %% ── Clients → Edge ────────────────────────────────────────────
    Web & Android & Admin -->|HTTPS| Edge

    %% ── Edge routing ──────────────────────────────────────────────
    Edge -->|API requests| Zuplo
    Edge <-->|Media CDN delivery| R2
    R2 -.->|Image transform at edge| ImgResize

    %% ── Gateway → API ─────────────────────────────────────────────
    Zuplo -->|Validated + rate-limited| ASPNET

    %% ── API ↔ Data ────────────────────────────────────────────────
    ASPNET <-->|Queries / writes| Mongo
    ASPNET <-->|Cache reads/writes| Redis

    %% ── Auth ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    ASPNET <-->|Validate Firebase ID tokens| FirebaseAuth
    Web & Android & Admin <-->|Sign-in · OAuth flows| FirebaseAuth

    %% ── Direct media upload (bypass API) ──────────────────────────
    Web & Android -->|Presigned PUT upload| R2

    %% ── Background workers ────────────────────────────────────────
    VidWorker <-->|Job status| Mongo
    VidWorker -->|Transcoded output| R2
    NotifWorker -->|Send push message| FCM
    FCM -->|Push notification| Android & Web
    NewsletterWorker <-->|Mark synced| Mongo
    NewsletterWorker -->|POST subscriber| Beehiiv
    CleanupWorker <-->|Find expired media| Mongo
    CleanupWorker -->|Delete orphaned objects| R2

    %% ── Observability ─────────────────────────────────────────────
    ASPNET -->|Errors · traces · performance| Sentry
    ASPNET -->|Prometheus metrics| Grafana

    %% ── Transactional email ───────────────────────────────────────
    ASPNET -->|Send email| Postmark

    %% ── Analytics (client-side only) ──────────────────────────────
    Web & Android -->|Analytics events| GA

    %% ── Compliance widgets ────────────────────────────────────────
    Termly -.->|Consent banner embedded| Web
    Termly -.->|Consent banner embedded| Admin

    %% ── Real-time upgrade path (post-MVP) ────────────────────────
    ASPNET -.->|"post-MVP: SSE / WebSocket"| SSE
    SSE -.->|"post-MVP: push to clients"| Web & Android

    %% ── CI/CD pipeline ────────────────────────────────────────────
    GitHub -->|Triggers| GHActions
    GHActions -->|Push Docker image| AppPlatform
    AppPlatform -->|Runs container| ASPNET
    GHActions -->|Apply changes| Terraform
